<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddd52fd7b-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06" identifier="/us/usc/t12/s5328"><num value="5328">§ 5328.</num><heading> Council funding</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any expenses of the Council shall be treated as expenses of, and paid by, the Office of Financial Research.</p>
